noticeDescription:
NOTICE OF PASSING OF BY-LAW 157-2022

 

Take notice that the Council of the City of Toronto has passed By-law 157-2022 to designate the property at 103 Heath Street West (Ward 12 Toronto-St. Paul’s) as being of cultural heritage value or interest.
